  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>Our Terms &amp; Conditions are viewable as PDF document(s). To view a PDF document you need to have a suitable reader program installed on your computer this usually means installing Adobe Reader. You may already have it installed on your computer. If not, the software is free and downloadable from <a rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" href="http://get.adobe.com/reader/" target="_blank">Adobe's website</a>.</p>
