<p><a data-udi="umb://document/af6732218b174bf898c6ed30f1d320ec" href="/{localLink:umb://document/af6732218b174bf898c6ed30f1d320ec}" title="Booking Conditions">Booking Conditions including Package Travel &amp; Linked Travel Regulations</a> (covering Ski &amp; Snowboarding, Lakes &amp; Mountains, Italy, Tours &amp; Multi-Centres, Lapland &amp; Santa Breaks)</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/ace4cf8381e54505b36b180dcc077f1a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ace4cf8381e54505b36b180dcc077f1a}" title="Important Information">Important Information</a></p>
<p> </p>
<p>Many of the flights and flight-inclusive holidays displayed on our website are financially protected by the ATOL scheme. But ATOL protection does not apply to all holiday and travel services listed on this website. Please ask us to confirm what protection may apply to your booking. If you do not receive an ATOL Certificate then the booking will not be ATOL protected. If you do receive an ATOL Certificate but all the parts of your trip are not listed on it, those parts will not be ATOL protected. Please see our booking conditions for information, or for more information about financial protection and the ATOL Certificate go to: <a rel="noopener" href="http://www.atol.org.uk/atolcertificate" target="_blank">www.atol.org.uk/atolcertificate</a>.</p>]]></bodyText>
